step.command:
echo rename-project
.bset env "RMX_BL=`cleartool lsstream -fmt %[found_bls]Np -cview | fgrep MCMS | tail -1`"
.retag ${RMX_BL}-BF.$B

echo cleanup
.bset env "num = $[ $B - $KEEP_HISTORY ]" .bset env "dir =../BUILD_$num"
# check existence of a directory to clean up if [ ! -d $dir ]; then echo directory $dir is cleaned up already exit 0 fi
# remove CC view if view directory exist if [ -d $dir/$BUILD_PATH ]; then
echo cd $dir/$BUILD_PATH cd $dir/$BUILD_PATH
echo ls -1 -d ${CC_VIEW_NAME_PREFIX}* | tail -1 echo remove view $CT rmview `ls -1 -d ${CC_VIEW_NAME_PREFIX}* | tail -1`
cd - fi
echo rm -rf $dir rm -rf $dir

echo create-view
echo "mkdir -p $BUILD_PATH" mkdir -p $BUILD_PATH
cd $BUILD_PATH
echo "$CT mkview -snapshot -tag $CC_VIEW_NAME -stream $CC_STREAM_NAME -stgloc Views $CC_VIEW_NAME" $CT mkview -snapshot -tag $CC_VIEW_NAME -stream $CC_STREAM_NAME -stgloc Views $CC_VIEW_NAME
cd $CC_VIEW_NAME
echo "$CT update -add_loadrules vob/MCMS/Main vob/MIG/Schemas vob/COMMON/IpMc" $CT update -add_loadrules vob/MCMS/Main vob/MCMS/McmIncld vob/MIG/Schemas vob/COMMON/IpMc
cd vob
# update view with main components echo "$CT update -f -ove" $CT update -f -ove

echo create-view-test echo build test environment, step create-view should be disabled
mkdir -p $MCMS_MAIN_PATH cd $MCMS_MAIN_PATH/.. rmdir Main ln -sf $DRABKIN_MAIN_PATH Main

echo verify-files
# check existence of the Main directory if [ ! -d $MCMS_MAIN_PATH ]; then echo directory $MCMS_MAIN_PATH is not exist exit -1 fi
if [ ! -e $MCMS_MAIN_PATH/Scripts/Cleanup.sh ]; then echo file $MCMS_MAIN_PATH/Scripts/Cleanup.sh is not exist exit -1 fi
# check existence of the AutoTestScripts directory if [ ! -d $AT_TOOLS_PATH ]; then echo directory $AT_TOOLS_PATH is not exist exit -1 fi
# check existence of the BuildTestEnv.sh file if [ ! -f $AT_TOOLS_PATH/BuildTestEnv.sh ]; then echo directory $AT_TOOLS_PATH/BuildTestEnv.sh is not exist exit -1 fi

echo build-project
cd $MCMS_MAIN_PATH
Scripts/Cleanup.sh
make active make -j50

echo run-report
#$AT_TOOLS_PATH/RunReport.sh $RESULT_PATH $AT_TOOLS_PATH $CC_VERSION
echo $AT_TOOLS_PATH/night_run_report.sh $RESULT_PATH $RESULT_PATH $AT_TOOLS_PATH tmpUdib $AT_MAIL_ADDR Carmel $RESULT_PATH $CC_VERSION $AT_TOOLS_PATH/night_run_report.sh $RESULT_PATH $RESULT_PATH $AT_TOOLS_PATH tmpUdib $AT_MAIL_ADDR Carmel $RESULT_PATH $CC_VERSION
